  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to compare active immunotherapy (OPT-822/OPT-821) with PBS in
      combination with low dose cyclophosphamide, in post-treated metastatic breast cancer subjects
      with stable disease or response to treatment.
    </textblock>
